Job Description
Looking for Software Developer,1. Have a strong Knowledge in Java, J2ee, C, C++ Algorithm.2. Develop, build and support a fast evolving product.3. Good Analytical and logical skills.4. Deliver high quality products.5. 0.3+ years of software development (Java,C,C++,C#,J2EE preferred)B.TECH or M.TECH in Computer Science from premier institute (or equivalent self-training)A strong foundation in computer science, with strong competencies in end to end development.
