Company profile:
Mount Talent Consulting has established itself as one of India s leading global HR Consulting firm focusing on HR services and solutions, recruitments and knowledge services (trainings and assessments). We have earned a reputation in talent and career management through sustained excellence in execution & responsiveness. Our specialty includes turnkey assignments and setting up teams from the scratch. The scope of our capabilities and solutions are unmatched with multifaceted services which set us apart in the industry. Mount Talent Consulting provides seamless solutions irrespective of the industry in which our clients exist.
